  "description": "Replace traditional villagers with the adorable Otters from DEDsafio!",
  "body": "![Sinnelar - Nutria DEDsafio 2](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/nutria-dedsafio-2/showcases/nutria-dedsafio-2-village-showcase.png)\n\n<b>Texture pack replaces villagers with otters from \"DEDSAFIO 2\".</b>\n<br/>\nIt has all jobs and villager variants, except illagers.\n\n<b>This texture pack needs Optifine's Custom Entity Models (CEM) for proper model loading.</b>\n<br/>\n<b>IT WILL NOT WORK PROPERLY WITHOUT THIS FEATURE!</b>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://optifine.net/downloads\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/nutria-dedsafio-2/ui/b-of-d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\"/>\n</a>\n\n<b>REQUIRED OPTIONS:</b>\n<br/>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/nutria-dedsafio-2/ui/g-cf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"540\"/>\n\nAs an alternative to Optifine, you can use <b>Entity Model Features (EMF)</b> and <b>Entity Texture Features (ETF)</b>.\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/nutria-dedsafio-2/ui/b-emf-d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\"/>\n</a>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/nutria-dedsafio-2/ui/b-etf-d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\"/>\n</a>\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=3122\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener nofollow\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Sinnelar/sinnelar-assets/heads/main/sinnelar-affiliates/sparked-host-promo-code-2026-minecraft-sinnelar.webp\" alt=\"Sparked Host Promo Code 2026 - 25% OFF Minecraft Server Hosting with Code Sinnelar\" width=\"100%\">\n  </a>\n</div>",
